<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-11-21T19:08:08-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-11-21T19:08:08-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-21T19:08:08-05:00</updated><title> Snap 称新墨西哥州故意与所谓的儿童掠夺者交朋友，然后指责该公司</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;快照徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/1hQanRpHWFE9TBVDaAr5xkdJA0I=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73739505/acastro_STK466_01.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;Alex Castro / The Verge 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;OSDubK&quot;>;Snap 讲述了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10 的基础/1/24259653/snap-new-mexico-ag-lawsuit-csam-kids-safety&quot;>;严厉的诉讼&lt;/a>;表明它系统地推荐青少年儿童掠夺者的账户是倒退的——该公司现在指责新墨西哥州总检察长在提出建议之前故意寻找此类账户。该公司表示，总检察长的案件是基于“严重失实陈述”和从 Snap 内部文件中挑选出来的。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;cUkrAj&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Snapchat 的“消失”信息使掠夺者很容易瞄准儿童，国家诉讼指控&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/5/24236722/snapchat-new-mexico-attorney-general-kids-online-safety-csam&quot;},{&quot;title&quot; ：“Snap 员工非常清楚该应用程序的儿童安全问题，新近公开的投诉说&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259653/snap-new-mexico-ag-lawsuit-csam-kids-safety&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div >;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;cDnTyS&quot;>;在周四提交的驳回动议中，Snap 表示 AG Raúl Torrez 的投诉“明显虚假”指控，尤其是歪曲其自己的卧底调查，总检察长办公室在调查中创建了一个 14 年前的诱饵账户。托雷兹指控 Snap 误导用户有关...的信息，从而违反了该州的不公平做法和公害法。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/21/24302767 /snap-new-mexico-attorney-general-motion-dismiss-child-exploitation&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/21/24302767/snap-new-mexico-attorney-general-motion-dismiss-child-exploitation" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/21/24302767/snap-new-mexico-attorney-general-motion-dismiss-child-exploitation</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-21T18:57:53-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-21T18:57:53-05:00</updated><title>最好的 iPhone</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;带有图形背景的各种型号的 iPhone 16。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/52vtvsLAoZdwZwYEDPCaqUbQUUw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn. vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72025718/247288_iPhone_Buying_Guides_2_CVirginia.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;人工智能时代的新 iPhone。&lt;/em>; |图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;无论您想要续航数天的电池还是最优惠的价格，我们都为您提供了一些您会喜欢的 iPhone 推荐。&lt;/p >; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-21T18:49:43-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-21T18:49:43-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2024 年黑色星期五指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色星期五和网络星期一期间销售的各种科技产品的图形拼贴。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/34PpCUfFqfk99i3Nb5yLmPZ7sow=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-c dn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73700761/247350_CMBF_PACKAGE_ART_CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p class=&quot;p--has-dropcap&quot; id=&quot;lujmaC&quot;>;如今，黑色星期五不再是一个单一的节日一天的购物假期，因为它是一个不断扩大、长达数月的活动，通常早在十月就开始了。曾经成为报纸头条新闻和商店外暴徒关注的 24 小时特惠闪电战已不复存